## Overview
FoodEZ is a web application that connects campus event organizers with students to reduce food waste. It allows event admins to post available food, and notifies students in real-time.

## Main Features
- Admin Sign Up and Sign In
- Student Sign Up
- Authentication (with SJSU email validation)
- Food form submission (date, time, building, description)
- SMS notifications to students

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: Next.js, Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Next.js API routes
- **Database**: (optional or in-memory)
- **Deployment**: Localhost (or live if hosted)

## Target Users
- SJSU Faculty (Admin)
- SJSU Students
